
NOTE: Position-{applys to Left,Right,Top,bottom}


Static- it has default value & does not apply top,bottom,right,left&z-index.

Relative- its place will be occpiued so                                                                
                                                                                                    <!-- ctrl+alt+downarrow  to copy a p-->
<!-- shift+alt+f=in one line -->


Absolute- its place will not be occpiued 


Fixed- its Position will bee fixed on the screen even if you scroll down the screen  it applys move all over the body 


Sticky- its Position will bee Sticky on the screen even for a particular section  you scroll down the screen it applys for section 

Position Offsets- Moving its Position left, right,top,bottom.
  
